OL,3,CEarly referral of Noah case to
OL,4,Cspecialist unit 'unusual but justified'
OL,6,FLocal police were "justified" in
OL,7,Felevating Noah Donohoe's investigation
OL,8,Fto the PSNI's criminal investigation
OL,9,Fdepartment (CID) at an early stage, an
OL,10,Finquest has heard.
OL,12,FA police witness reiterated his view
OL,13,Fto Belfast Coroner's Court that
OL,14,Fofficers had "gripped" the seriousness
OL,15,Fof the search for Noah at an early
OL,16,Fpoint.
OL,18,FThe inquest into the death of the
OL,19,Fschoolboy, which is being heard with a
OL,20,Fjury, is now in its seventh week.
OL,26,@nD@SOUnD@]O]vD@NOUvD@VO]
