CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773280992
OL,3,CEarly referral of Noah case to
OL,4,Cspecialist unit 'unusual but justified'
OL,6,FNoah, a pupil at St Malachy's College,
OL,7,Fwas 14 when his naked body was found
OL,8,Fin a storm drain tunnel in north
OL,9,FBelfast in June 2020, six days after
OL,10,Fhe left home on his bike to meet two
OL,11,Ffriends in the Cavehill area of the
OL,12,Fcity.
OL,14,FA post-mortem examination found the
OL,15,Fcause of death was drowning.
OL,17,FThe court was told that PSNI Chief
OL,18,FInspector Robinson was experienced in
OL,19,Fmissing persons investigations and had
OL,20,Ftrained hundreds of officers.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773280992
OL,3,CEarly referral of Noah case to
OL,4,Cspecialist unit 'unusual but justified'
OL,6,FDonal Lunney KC, counsel for the PSNI,
OL,7,Ftook Mr Robinson through the police
OL,8,Flog from the early hours of June 22
OL,9,F2020 highlighting points at which
OL,10,Frecords had been made of handovers
OL,11,Fbetween officers.
OL,13,FThe police log showed that Noah had
OL,14,Fbeen deemed high risk at 12.47am on
OL,15,FJune 22, hours after he was reported
OL,16,Fmissing at 9.44pm on June 21.
OL,18,FMr Robinson said at an operational
OL,19,Fhandover every sergeant is looking for
OL,20,Fa number of things "among those would
OL,21,Fbe a high-risk missing person".
OL,26,@|D@TOU}D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
