PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773280992
OL,3,CEarly referral of Noah case to
OL,4,Cspecialist unit 'unusual but justified'
OL,6,FLater Mr Lunney flagged that CID,
OL,7,Fwhich specialises in investigating
OL,8,Fserious, complex and organised crime,
OL,9,Fhad been asked for input in the case
OL,10,Fas early as Tuesday June 23 which Mr
OL,11,FRobinson agreed would have been
OL,12,Funusual.
OL,14,FHe said this fact is "relevant to grip
OL,15,Fand ownership" of the investigation by
OL,16,FPSNI but is "probably not relevant to
OL,17,Foutcome".
OL,26,@vD@VOUwD@NO]xD@MOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
