CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773280992
OL,3,CEarly referral of Noah case to
OL,4,Cspecialist unit 'unusual but justified'
OL,6,FThe review went on to state that this
OL,7,Fdecision was "justified" because the
OL,8,Finvestigation was becoming more
OL,9,Fcomplex" for a number of reasons,
OL,10,Fincluding that "possibilities that may
OL,11,Fhave been plausible at an earlier
OL,12,Fstage become more remote" such as Noah
OL,13,Fbeing at Cavehill.
